title: David Hurley - Wikipedia
snippet: General David John Hurley (born 26 August 1953) is an Australian former politician and military officer. A senior officer in the Australian Army, he served as the 27th governor-general of Australia from 2019 to 2024. He was previously the 38th governor of New South Wales from 2014 to 2019.

title: David Hurley facts for kids
snippet: After leaving the army in June 2014, Hurley became the Governor of New South Wales. He took over from Marie Bashir in October 2014. His time as Governor ended in May 2019. He was then chosen by Queen Elizabeth II to be the Governor-General.
